description: May your next party be a marvelous occasion, thanks to the tasty treats and sensational service courtesy of Mae’s Mobile Snack Bar. This rad retro truck will haul all the fun and flavor straight to your door with their phenomenal menu that includes all-beef gourmet hot dogs, fresh popped popcorn, cotton candy, and more!If you’re feelin’ the Florida heat, they even carry refreshingly sweet Hawaiian shaved ice too. So when planning your next event, you don’t have to think twice, Mae’s Mobile Snack Bar is a dream come true!
name: Mae's Mobile Snack Bar
